{"tid":1894442,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"米斯捷拒絕加盟滙控接任行政總裁","createTime":"2020-02-24T02:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T08:56:34.000Z","uid":10757,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"57d205d2bfa70b5e6f8112878d5866f461ece336","tid":1894442,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:24:16.000Z","msg":"有報道引述消息人士指，意大利最大銀行裕信(UniCredit)行政總裁米斯捷(Jean-Pierre Mustier)，已拒絕轉投滙控，米斯捷盛傳是滙豐新行政總裁的熱門人選。金融時報報道指，米斯捷星期日致電滙豐主席杜嘉祺(Mark Tucker)，表明無意接任滙豐行政總裁一職。另外，路透引述消息人士報道指，裕信將會發表聲明，指米斯捷會繼續留任裕信。金融時報早前引述消息人士指，米斯捷與現任臨時行政總裁祈耀年(Noel Quinn)競爭滙控行政總裁一職。滙豐上周公布業績時，表示仍在進行行政總裁正式人選的評選工作，預期會按照原定時間於6至12個月內作出委任。滙控今早股價微跌，報56.6元，跌幅不足0.1%。<br />\n<br />\n2020-02-24 10:03:17 (1)<br />\n<br />\nHSBC係咪在銀行界冇哂吸引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216546f69f8d29ef21ec1f80d7ef5a32137c15b0","tid":1894442,"uid":321977,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:25:33.000Z","msg":"做大佬但無得話事，搵支那狗做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7543263a7aafcdda40a31628072d5704f26d0698","tid":1894442,"uid":108337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:25:55.000Z","msg":"自從比人ban左係伊朗洗黑錢，就好似冇咩生意"},{"pid":"ee49e3afcfc23a77435a2a62c438348eaf109939","tid":1894442,"uid":68689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"216546f69f8d29ef21ec1f80d7ef5a32137c15b0","tid":1894442,"uid":321977,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:25:33.000Z","msg":"做大佬但無得話事，搵支那狗做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:27:08.000Z","msg":"支那狗做緊啦"},{"pid":"2bce4964e33e4793fd88adcf7f20cf45ee76d5c5","tid":1894442,"uid":5378,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:27:24.000Z","msg":"銀行轉會轉到踢波咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455